 <preface>
  <title>Preface</title>
  <para>
   This manual will eventually describe how to install, use, and extend Project
   Manager.
  </para>
  <para>
   If you encounter problems then please reach out on
   <link xlink:href="https://matrix.to/#/%23project-manager:matrix.org">the
   Project Manager Matrix room</link>. If your problem is caused by a bug in
   Project Manager then it should be reported on the
   <link xlink:href="https://github.com/sellout/project-manager/issues">Project
   Manager issue tracker</link>.
  </para>
  <note>
   <para>
    Commands prefixed with <literal>$ sudo</literal> have to be run as root, either
    requiring to login as root user or temporarily switching to it using
    <literal>sudo</literal> for example.
   </para>
  </note>
 </preface>
